IRS990EZ.PrimaryExemptPurposeTxt: THE SPECIFIC CHARITABLE PURPOSE OF THIS CORPORATION IS TO ADDRESS HEALTH DISPARITIES BY DEVELOPING LEADERS IN SERVICE: INDIVIDUALS WHO ARE DEDICATED TO AND SKILLED IN MEETING THE HEALTH NEEDS OF UNDERSERVED COMMUNITIES AND WHOSE EXAMPLE INFLUENCES AND INSPIRES OTHERS WITHIN THE MEANING OF SECTION 501(C)(3) OF THE INTERNAL REVENUE CODE OF 1986, AS AMENDED,OR CORRESPONDING SECTION OF ANY FUTURE FEDERAL TAX CODE.

ProgramSrvcAccomplishmentGrp.DescriptionProgramSrvcAccomTxt: TO IMPROVE THE HEALTH OF VULNERABLE PEOPLE AND MINORITY POPULATIONS NOW AND IN THE FUTURE BY DEVELOPING A CORPS OF LEADERS IN SERVICE-SCHWEITZER FELLOWSHIP PROFESSIONALS SKILLED IN CREATING POSITIVE CHANGE WITHIN THE HEALTH AND SERVICE SYSTEM OF THE LOCAL COMMUNITIES THROUGH COMMUNITY-BASED, MENTORED DIRECT SERVICE;SUSTAINABLE DEVELOPMENT PROGRAM AND IMPLEMENTATION; AND A MULTIDISCIPLINARY,REFLECTIVE LEADERSHIP DEVELOPMENT PROGRAM IN ORDER TO BUILD A COMMUNITY CAPACITY AND A PROFESSIONALLY TRAINED WORKFORCE.
